<div class="content">
		<h3>Educational Videos</h3>
		<p class="width80">The <a href=http://boston.lti.cs.cmu.edu/Services/clueweb12_render/getresource.cgi/renderpage.cgi?id=clueweb12-0201wb-47-32929&c=false>Office of Public Information</a> for Jehovah&#8217;s Witnesses is pleased to provide the media with broadcast versions of the videos shown below, in DVCPRO, Beta or VHS format.</p>
		<div class="video">
		<img src="http://www.jw%2Dmedia.org/images/vid/vid01ect.jpg" width="80" height="60" alt="Doctors performing a surgery">
		<p class="title"><a href=http://boston.lti.cs.cmu.edu/Services/clueweb12_render/getresource.cgi/renderpage.cgi?id=clueweb12-0202wb-14-15839&c=false>No Blood&#8212;Medicine Meets the Challenge</a></p>
		<p>This documentary presents  case histories along with fascinating interviews to help viewers understand what  nonblood alternatives are and how they work. </p>
		</div>

		<div class="video">
		<img src="http://www.jw%2Dmedia.org/images/vid/vid02ect.jpg" width="80" height="60" alt="A heartbeat">
		<p class="title"><a href=http://boston.lti.cs.cmu.edu/Services/clueweb12_render/getresource.cgi/renderpage.cgi?id=clueweb12-0202wb-14-15840&c=false>Transfusion-Alternative Strategies&#8212;Simple, Safe,  Effective</a></p>
		<p>In a spirit of respect and cooperation,  Jehovah&#8217;s Witnesses desire to share with medical professionals everywhere some  of the findings of the leading medical authorities in regard to  transfusion-alternative strategies.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="video">
		<img src="http://www.jw%2Dmedia.org/images/vid/vid03ect.jpg" width="80" height="60" alt="A doctor, a judge, and a lawyer">
		<p class="title"><a href=http://boston.lti.cs.cmu.edu/Services/clueweb12_render/getresource.cgi/renderpage.cgi?id=clueweb12-0202wb-06-33527&c=false>Transfusion-Alternative Health Care&#8212;Meeting Patient  Needs and Rights</a></p>
		<p>Health-care professionals are keenly interested in meeting each patient&#8217;s  medical needs. Thus, they welcome new therapies and approaches that can help  them do this.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="video">
		<img src="http://www.jw%2Dmedia.org/images/vid/vid04ect.jpg" width="80" height="60" alt="A open Bible">
		<p class="title"><a href=http://boston.lti.cs.cmu.edu/Services/clueweb12_render/getresource.cgi/renderpage.cgi?id=clueweb12-0201wb-96-28597&c=false>The Bible&#8212;Its Power in Your Life</a></p>
		<p>Listen as real people tell you the power for good that the Bible has been in  their lives. See how much better life is for those who open their hearts and  minds to the Bible&#8217;s wisdom.		</p>
		</div>


		<div class="video">
		<img src="http://www.jw%2Dmedia.org/images/vid/vid05ect.jpg" width="80" height="60" alt="Jehovah's Witnesses from the former Soviet Union">
		<p class="title"><a href=http://boston.lti.cs.cmu.edu/Services/clueweb12_render/getresource.cgi/renderpage.cgi?id=clueweb12-0202wb-14-15841&c=false>Faithful Under Trials&#8212;Jehovah&#8217;s Witnesses in the Soviet  Union</a></p>
		<p>On three nights in early April 1951, thousands of Jehovah&#8217;s Witnesses from  Ukraine, Moldavia, and the Baltic lands&#8212;men, women, and children&#8212;were loaded  into boxcars and exiled to Siberia. Historians and eyewitnesses recount the  enlightening and inspiring story of Jehovah&#8217;s Witnesses in the former Soviet  Union.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="video">
		<img src="http://www.jw%2Dmedia.org/images/vid/vid06ect.jpg" width="80" height="60" alt="Prison uniform for Jehovah's Witnesses during Hitler's regime">
		<p class="title"><a href=http://boston.lti.cs.cmu.edu/Services/clueweb12_render/getresource.cgi/renderpage.cgi?id=clueweb12-0201wb-36-27717&c=false>Jehovah&#8217;s Witnesses Stand Firm Against Nazi Assault</a></p>
		<p>As the Nazi killing machine engulfed Europe with terror, thousands of Jehovah&#8217;s  Witnesses suffered brutal persecution. In this video, 10 historians from Europe  and North America, and more than 20 Witness survivors, join in relating a story  of courage and triumph that must be told.</p>
		</div>

